{"en":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"That which is considered to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/exist\" title=\"exist\">exist</a> as a separate <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/entity\" title=\"entity\">entity</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/object\" title=\"object\">object</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/quality\" title=\"quality\">quality</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/concept\" title=\"concept\">concept</a>."},{"definition":"A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/word\" title=\"word\">word</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/symbol\" title=\"symbol\">symbol</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/sign\" title=\"sign\">sign</a>, or other <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/referent\" title=\"referent\">referent</a> that can be used to refer to any entity."},{"definition":"An individual object or distinct entity."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt48\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span>\n<ol><li>Whatever can be <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/own\" title=\"own\">owned</a>.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/corporeal\" title=\"corporeal\">Corporeal</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/object\" title=\"object\">object</a>.</li></ol>"},{"definition":"Whatever can be <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/own\" title=\"own\">owned</a>."},{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/corporeal\" title=\"corporeal\">Corporeal</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/object\" title=\"object\">object</a>."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt49\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/possessions\" title=\"possessions\">Possessions</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/equipment\" title=\"equipment\">equipment</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/stuff\" title=\"stuff\">stuff</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/gear\" title=\"gear\">gear</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Hold on, let me just grab my <b>things</b>."}],"examples":["Hold on, let me just grab my <b>things</b>."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt51\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> The <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/latest\" title=\"latest\">latest</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/fad\" title=\"fad\">fad</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/fashion\" title=\"fashion\">fashion</a>."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt53\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/custom\" title=\"custom\">custom</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/practice\" title=\"practice\">practice</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Cheek kissing is a French <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> you get used to it after a while."}],"examples":["Cheek kissing is a French <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> you get used to it after a while."]},{"definition":""},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\"></span> A genuine concept, entity or phenomenon; something that actually exists (often contrary to expectation or belief). <style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r90144991\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles\" about=\"#mwt58\">.mw-parser-output .defdate{font-size:smaller}</style>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Q<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> Bacon pie<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span> Is that a <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span> A<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> Yes, I checked into it, and it's a <b>thing</b>. Some people are even connoisseurs about it."}],"examples":["Q<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> Bacon pie<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span> Is that a <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span> A<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> Yes, I checked into it, and it's a <b>thing</b>. Some people are even connoisseurs about it."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt64\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A unit or container, usually containing consumable <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/good\" title=\"good\">goods</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Could you get me a <b>thing</b> of apple juice at the store<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>"},{"example":"I just ate a whole <b>thing</b> of jelly beans."}],"examples":["Could you get me a <b>thing</b> of apple juice at the store<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>","I just ate a whole <b>thing</b> of jelly beans."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt70\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/problem\" title=\"problem\">problem</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/dilemma\" title=\"dilemma\">dilemma</a>, or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/complicating\" title=\"complicating\">complicating</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/factor\" title=\"factor\">factor</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"The car looks cheap, but the <b>thing</b> is, I have doubts about its safety."},{"example":"That's the <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> we don't know where he is."}],"examples":["The car looks cheap, but the <b>thing</b> is, I have doubts about its safety.","That's the <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> we don't know where he is."]},{"definition":""},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/penis\" title=\"penis\">penis</a>."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt77\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/vulva\" title=\"vulva\">vulva</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/vagina\" title=\"vagina\">vagina</a>."},{"definition":"A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/living\" title=\"living\">living</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/being\" title=\"being\">being</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/creature\" title=\"creature\">creature</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"you <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/poor_thing#English\" title=\"poor thing\">poor <b>thing</b></a>"},{"example":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/sweet_young_thing#English\" title=\"sweet young thing\">sweet young <b>thing</b></a>"},{"example":"she's a funny old <b>thing</b>, but her heart's in the right place"},{"example":"I met a pretty blond <b>thing</b> at the bar"}],"examples":["you <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/poor_thing#English\" title=\"poor thing\">poor <b>thing</b></a>","<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/sweet_young_thing#English\" title=\"sweet young thing\">sweet young <b>thing</b></a>","she's a funny old <b>thing</b>, but her heart's in the right place","I met a pretty blond <b>thing</b> at the bar"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt83\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used after a noun to refer dismissively to the situation surrounding the noun's referent.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Oh yeah, I'm supposed to promote that vision <b>thing</b>."}],"examples":["Oh yeah, I'm supposed to promote that vision <b>thing</b>."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt86\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> That which is favoured; personal <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/preference\" title=\"preference\">preference</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"it's not really my <b>thing</b>"}],"examples":["it's not really my <b>thing</b>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt92\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> One's typical routine, habits, or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/manner\" title=\"manner\">manner</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"let me do my <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span>&nbsp; I'm here doing my <b>thing</b>"}],"examples":["let me do my <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span>&nbsp; I'm here doing my <b>thing</b>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt95\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A public <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/assembly\" title=\"assembly\">assembly</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/judicial\" title=\"judicial\">judicial</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/council\" title=\"council\">council</a> in a <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Germanic\" title=\"Germanic\">Germanic</a> country."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt98\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/romantic\" title=\"romantic\">romantic</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/relationship\" title=\"relationship\">relationship</a>."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt100\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/romantic\" title=\"romantic\">romantic</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/couple\" title=\"couple\">couple</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Are John and Jennifer a <b>thing</b> again<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span> I thought they broke up."}],"examples":["Are John and Jennifer a <b>thing</b> again<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span> I thought they broke up."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt102\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt103\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Alternative form of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"en\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/ting#English\" title=\"ting\">ting</a></i></span></span>."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt104\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> Girl; attractive woman.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Look at the <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/nyash#English\" title=\"nyash\">nyash</a> on that <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>"}],"examples":["Look at the <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/nyash#English\" title=\"nyash\">nyash</a> on that <b>thing</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>"]}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Verb","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt182\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> To express as a thing; to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/reify\" title=\"reify\">reify</a>."}]}],"other":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Khumi Chin","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/firewood\" title=\"firewood\">firewood</a>"}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Middle English","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/thing#English\" class=\"mw-selflink-fragment\">thing</a>"}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Mizo","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/tree\" title=\"tree\">tree</a>"},{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/wood\" title=\"wood\">wood</a>"},{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/firewood\" title=\"firewood\">firewood</a>"}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Old High German","definitions":[{"definition":"(Early) <span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt212\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">alternative form of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"goh\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/ding#Old_High_German\" title=\"ding\">ding</a></i></span></span>"}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Old Saxon","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"en\" about=\"#mwt223\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/thing#English\" class=\"mw-selflink-fragment\">thing</a></span>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/object\" title=\"object\">object</a>"},{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/matter\" title=\"matter\">matter</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/case\" title=\"case\">case</a>"}]}]}